 ("nm7629471", null, null, null, null, null, null, null, "Sean Renzetti was born in Hollywood, Florida. His career began in his early years studying at performing arts schools. He received training, touching on many different fields of work in the entertainment world. In his teens, Sean was given his first taste of a professional setting when he was cast in his own show on educational television. Being the host of the show, it gave him a glimpse of the work done behind the camera. This is where he fell in love with the process and what it takes to create the magic in film and television.Sean started his directing career doing local stage performances around south Florida. His work was found in community theaters, clubs, state fairs, and youth competitions. Throughout his career, Sean has won numerous awards for his acting, writing, and directing. Most recently, he brought home 6 wins and 5 official selection with his short film \"Bang Bang Goes the Gun!\" Renzetti is most known for being the front man of the touring group, \"The Drive Home.\" The band reached its peak as it shared the stage with top billing groups such as The Backstreet Boys, Sister Hazel, Good Charlotte, and Finger Eleven.Sean Renzetti has a passion to entertain - intertwined with his need to help others and give more than he takes, you find a true artist. He has since been working toward a career that gives him purpose and the ability to give back to greater society. In that, was the birth of TRUSETTE Entertainment.", null, null, "Sean", null, "Renzetti", null, null, "Sean Renzetti"),
