 ("nm4984337", null, null, null, null, null, null, null, "Garth Wynne-Jones is a multi-disciplined artist - Actor, Record Producer and DJ. He was born and educated in South East England, attending two boarding schools from the age of 7, St Piran's (which he loathed) and Reading Blue Coats (which he loved). He earned his degree at Westminster University in London before emigrating to America in 1990. As world renowned DJ Garth, he rose to prominence with the Wicked Sound System, spreading rave culture to America via San Francisco. He owns and records for dance music labels Grayhound, Wicked and Golden Goose Records. His acting debut was in the 2013 feature film Speed Dragon (2013) which premiered at Cannes and won Best Feature Film at the NY International Independent Film Festival. He lives in Los Angeles with his dog and daughter, where he continues to work as a DJ, film and voice actor.", null, null, "Garth", null, "Wynne-Jones", null, null, "Garth Wynne-Jones"),
